Available operators

W&B supports the following operators for line plot expressions:

Category| Operators  
---|---  
Arithmetic| `+`, `-`, `*`, `/`, `%` (modulo), `**` (exponent)  
Comparison| `==`, `!=`, `===`, `!==`, `<`, `>`, `<=`, `>=`  
Bitwise| `|`, `^`, `&`, `<<`, `>>`, `>>>`  
Logical| `||` , `&&`  
  
